snippet.title: Critical Role
snippet.description:
What started as a home roleplaying game in 2012 has evolved into to a bit of a phenomenon. In June 2021, Critical Role concluded its second campaign with nearly 1,000 hours of storytelling across both campaigns, crafted by Game Master Matthew Mercer and fellow accomplished voice actors Travis Willingham, Marisha Ray, Taliesin Jaffe, Ashley Johnson, Sam Riegel, Liam O’Brien, and Laura Bailey.

On our YouTube channel, you will find new content created with love by the Critical Role team. If you’re looking for the tales of Vox Machina (Campaign 1) or the Mighty Nein (Campaign 2), you can find both on our YouTube homepage playlists. You can catch Critical Role live on Thursdays at 7pm Pacific at twitch.tv/criticalrole and youtube.com/criticalrole. 

Our profile icon features our map designed by Deven Rue and our header image features photography by Anna Azarov.
